Name: cherry blossom fleet
About the game: 「In 1946, a full-scale counteroffensive operation was launched against the Japanese army, which has vast Pacific Ocean areas. Shoot the enemy fleet, break in the iron-clad Pacific defense line and Show the American spirit.」 This Game Is A top-down 2d Shooter Features Simple gameplay that follows the good old 2D shooting game system Three types of aircraft can be selected Each has features such as wide range type, centralized type, and high power type. Your ship is usually with a shot In addition, it has an emergency bomb and a support aircraft attack, Support aircraft attacks can be participated in the attack by using the Charge gauge. Support machines are also characterized by wide-range type, centralized type, and high-power type. By combining it with your own attack, you can make more efficient attacks.
